come to apply to stanford summer session as visiting undergraduates the stanford summer international honors program offers a convenient online application all applicants are required to pay a non refundable $75 application fee as part of the application process the stanford summer international honors program does not accept fee waivers learn more about our application requirements view the stanford summer international honors brochure keep in touch with stanford summer session join our email list stanford university home map & directions help stanford university summer session terms of use copyright complaints powered by eresources
